  "description": "A ***knowledge base*** is a collection of articles organized to help readers solve specific problems or answer specific questions. Unlike a [user guide](./user-guide.md), which follows a product's structure, a knowledge base is organized around the reader's questions — each article is a self-contained answer to one question or solution to one problem.",
